{"tid":434984,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"等左咁耐佢終於出現左","createTime":"2017-10-13T21:14:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-13T22:22:55.000Z","uid":144866,"like":0,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"5398d0196fbf597f20d34c20a773511054872228","tid":434984,"uid":144866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T21:14:01.000Z","msg":"我做左二十幾年人<br />\n呢個星期三我終於見到一個<br />\n符合曬我希望我將來女朋友有嘅嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我問佢𢲡左電話，佢都好直接二話不說就俾左我<br />\n我同佢傾左幾日whatapps 佢周不時仲用埋語音<br />\n已經約左下個星期三食飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但今日發現左佢已經有男朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n各位巴絲打，我仲應唔應該去好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢個遊戲應該點玩?<br />\n唔明點解佢仲可以咁直接<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9644405a8e527ac3ff3969f8e1eaf8968c74e771","tid":434984,"uid":8345,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T21:15:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"087d5d3299c897efe3684171edce608c3ddd8b3e","tid":434984,"uid":144866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T21:16:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>比個電話就代表想做你女朋友既話咁我應該好多女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n照有計傾，有冇咩特別，佢份人好似好直接"},{"pid":"d217b2b0dec9701611d9c919cfcc820d3e795a6c","tid":434984,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T21:16:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>比個電話就代表想做你女朋友既話咁我應該好多女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你真係好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e84b4046f67bc49396c2e990e9e0e5b24602db1","tid":434984,"uid":52477,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T21:17:36.000Z","msg":"你諗多左 你等既過程中個生態環境已經變左好多 知套思想好舊 但我唔會話你錯"},{"pid":"64581377a787322382739c0df77a6797108cbf21","tid